{"tid":2053550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武術》太極李小龍無法為父報仇了！中國武術中心緊急修法打假","createTime":"2020-06-06T11:13:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T11:14:42.000Z","uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"016f546f235ac43cfa844a80191ca5d8d386aef5","tid":2053550,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:13:34.000Z","msg":"〔記者梁偉銘／綜合報導〕號稱「太極界李小龍」的馬曉陽，恐怕無法為父報仇了！針對日前武術賽事引發各界關注，加上眾多打著「武林高手」名號的江湖人士破壞社會善良風氣，中國國家體育總局武術中心已發佈最新規定，希望「打假」亡羊補牢，避免類似醜聞持續發生。<br />\n<br />\n名氣響亮的「混元形意太極」掌門人馬保國，日前上擂台僅撐30秒，被業餘無名小卒3度擊倒，甚至慘遭KO昏迷送醫，引發各國媒體報導；高齡68歲的中國武術大師一敗成名，曾留學英國的寶貝兒子馬曉陽跟著爆紅，宣稱曾是老外眼中李小龍的他，不但詭異教拳影音笑點十足，還被網友鼓吹勇敢站出來打擂台，用蓋世神功替老爸討回顏面。<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3187893\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3187893&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=ee3ef103\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3187893&h=0b77a904\" target=\"_blank\">https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3187893</a><br />\n<br />\n名氣響亮的「混元形意太極」掌門人馬保國:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=94aQsvctFoI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D94aQsvctFoI&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=3550cc00\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=94aQsvctFoI</a>"},{"pid":"316ee0c465d004595f4aff34aa81860f8835f5c5","tid":2053550,"uid":30561,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:14:00.000Z","msg":"咁肥都叫李小龍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee86446bb2a63bb45e33d0cdcf3d1f847c73509","tid":2053550,"uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:14:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rnTASrbG61U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/lin